oscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week travel guide la fortuna waterfall\"><\/noscript><img width=\"238\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week travel guide la fortuna waterfall\" class=\"wp-image-77607 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1353px) 100vw, 1353px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35.jpg 1353w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-423x600.jpg 423w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-571x810.jpg 571w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-238x338.jpg 238w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-115x163.jpg 115w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-127x180.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-541x768.jpg 541w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-722x1024.jpg 722w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-761x1080.jpg 761w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-1015x1440.jpg 1015w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-300x426.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-600x851.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-150x213.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35-21x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211818\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-35.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-how-to-get-from-puerto-viejo-to-la-fortuna\">How to get from Puerto Viejo to La Fortuna<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<h5><strong>By car:<\/strong><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>The journey from Puerto Viejo to La Fortuna should take around 4.5 hours on well-paved roads. However, to avoid pothole damage, we recommend hiring a car with a bit more clearance from the ground.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27230859\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-34.jpg\" alt=\"4x4 rental costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"4x4 rental costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-77217 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27230859\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-34.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/27230859\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-34-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/