de-34.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h5><strong>By bus or shuttle:<\/strong><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>The journey from Puerto Viejo to La Fortuna is fairly long and not super accessible by public transport. You&#x2019;ll need to transfer buses in San Jose, which means the journey can take around 8-9 hours.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you don&#x2019;t have a car, the best option is to take a shared shuttle bus that leaves in the morning and takes around 6 hours. The cost of this is about 60 USD, but it&#x2019;s far less hassle than the public bus.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transport-puerto-viejo-la-fortuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a bus or shuttle to La Fortuna<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-where-to-stay-in-la-fortuna\">Where to Stay in La Fortuna<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>La Fortuna has excellent accommodation for all types of budget. However, you&#x2019;ll find the best accommodations and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/camping-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">campsites<\/a> just outside La Fortuna if you have your transport. If hot springs play a big part in your 2-week Costa Rica itinerary, consider staying in a hotel with hot springs that are also included in the nightly price. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/lafortuna-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Here are all your hotel options<\/a>)&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/lafortuna-casaluna\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Casa Luna Hotel &amp; Spa\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16170817\/293205329-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Casa Luna Hotel &amp; Spa<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"border: 4px solid red;\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Sangregado Lodge\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/16170825\/315393961-450x338.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Sangregado Lodge<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-6-of-2-weeks-in-costa-rica-la-fortuna\">Day 6 of 2 weeks in Costa Rica: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/la-fortuna\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">La Fortuna<\/a> <\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Spend one of the most magical days in La Fortuna, enjoying nature&#x2019;s very own playground! Wake up early and head for Arenal Volcano National Park, home to the country&#x2019;s most active volcano! Don&#x2019;t worry, though, rangers make sure to monitor the activity and close trails accordingly so you&#x2019;re always safe. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211322\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-29.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week travel guide arenal volcano\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week travel guide arenal volcano\" class=\"wp-image-77602 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211322\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-29.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211322\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-29-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211322\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-29-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211322\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-29-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03211322\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-29-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourh