urhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/23050219\/la-fortuna-arenal-volcano-5-1080x721.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>On your way, stop at Mistico Hanging Bridges, which are about a 30-minutes drive from La Fortuna. This fantastic jungle trail is about 3 km long and includes six adrenaline-pumping hanging bridges. From a height of 45 meters, you&#x2019;ll have the opportunity to walk across bridges suspended between the treetops, gaining the unique chance to see an abundance of wildlife. Don&#x2019;t forget to look out for the elusive red-eyed tree frog, an icon of Costa Rica!<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n<a class=\"block-googlemaps\" title=\"Get our Google Maps Legend\" data-maptype=\"Costa Rica \" href=\"\/shop\/google-maps\/costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            <div class=\"block-googlemaps__container\">\n                <div class=\"block-googlemaps__content\">\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__title\">Our Costa Rica  tips in your Google Maps?<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__text\">We made it easier for you! All our tips: favourite to do's, restaurants, hikes, secret spots &amp; more in Google Maps!<\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__button\">Shop our Maps <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <span class=\"block-googlemaps__notice\" style=\"display:none; font-size:12px; margin-top:15px;\">The map for this destination will be available soon. Thank you for your interest!<\/span>\n                <\/div>\n                <img class=\"block-googlemaps__image lazyload\" tempsrc=\"\/build\/images\/google-maps-banner-image.png\" alt=\"google maps phone\">\n            <\/div>\n        <\/a>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica travel guide Mistico Hanging Bridges\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica travel guide Mistico Hanging Bridges\" class=\"wp-image-77612 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212047\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-33-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-cont