apper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-77614 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212103\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-34.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-how-to-get-from-la-fortuna-to-monteverde\">How to get from La Fortuna to Monteverde<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<h5 id=\"h-by-car\"><strong>By car:<\/strong><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>Although La Fortuna and Monteverde look close on the map, the mammoth Lake Arenal separates the two villages. This means you need to drive around its parameter, which takes around 3 hours. However, luckily, it&#x2019;s a stunning drive, perhaps one of the nicest on your 2-week Costa Rica itinerary!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The roads around the lake to Santa Elena (Monteverde town) are all well-paved. Still, we recommend having a slightly more powerful car for the steep hills. (no 4&#xD7;4 needed to visit Monteverde).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide by car\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"costa rica 7 day travel guide by car\" class=\"wp-image-77053 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-150x100.jpg 150w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/25185125\/costa-rica-7-day-guide-11-1080x721.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h5 id=\"h-by-bus-or-shuttle\"><strong>By bus or shuttle:<\/strong><\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>Buses leave from La Fortuna to Monteverde, but they take around 7-8 hours. Additionally, you won&#x2019;t be able to visit the Mistico Hanging Bridges when traveling by bus. Alternatively, get a shared shuttle van for around 50-60 USD.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transport-lafortuna-monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book a bus or shuttle to Monteverde<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h5><strong>By boat<\/strong>:<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>Small ferries cross Lake Arenal, but they don&#x2019;t take transport. If you are traveling without transportation, this can be an excellent option to get to Monteverde. The journey takes around 2 &#x2013; 2.5 hours, and you&#x2019;ll get to enjoy a trip across the lake with beautiful views of the volcano; it&#x2019;s a unique way to travel! Prices start from 25 USD.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-where-to-stay-in-monteverde\">Where to Stay in Monteverde<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Monteverde offers numerous accommodation options, from cabins in the forest to hotels in Santa Elena. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/monteverde-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all your hotels options here<\/a>) <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/chira-glamping-monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Chira Glamping\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03224856\/chira-glamping-monteverde-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Chira Glamping<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/los-pinos-lodge-monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Los Pinos Lodge\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03224905\/los-pinos-lodge-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Los Pinos Lodge<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-8-monteverde\">Day 8: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Monteverde<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Welcome to Monteverde (Green Mountain), home to unique and rare cloud forests. In fact, cloud forests only make up 1% of all forests worldwide! These beautiful areas are given their name because of their high altitude, which causes mist and low-lying clouds to appear through the trees. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181215\/monteverde-costa-rica-5.jpg\" alt=\"colobri cafe monteverde\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colobri cafe monteverde\" class=\"wp-image-75200 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181215\/monteverde-costa-rica-5.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181215\/monteverde-costa-rica-5-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181215\/monteverde-costa-rica-5-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181215\/monteverde-costa-rica-5-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181215\/monteverde-costa-rica-5-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181215\/monteverde-costa-rica-5-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\