ir.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/02181304\/monteverde-costa-rica-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Explore the Monteverde or Santa Elena cloud forest trails, looking out for frogs, butterflies, insects, and monkeys (you can even see beautiful hummingbirds at a nearby cafe!). Take part in the exhilarating night walk experience at night, led by a knowledgeable local guide.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you&#x2019;re done exploring the cloud forests, enjoy more adventures among the beautiful Monteverde nature, from ziplining and canyoning to coffee tasting.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Read: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/monteverde\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Top things to do in Monteverde, Costa Rica<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week guide monteverde cloud forest\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week guide monteverde cloud forest\" class=\"wp-image-77624 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-150x188.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03213102\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-43.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-9-monteverde-to-manuel-antonio\">Day 9: Monteverde to Manuel Antonio<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Spend your morning enjoying the colorful butterfly garden at Monteverde before starting your trip south to Manuel Antonio. Manuel Antonio is a lovely coastal town surrounded by pristine, white-sand beaches, beautiful blue ocean, and lush jungle. Most importantly, it&#x2019;s home to Manuel Antonio National Park, known as one of the most beautiful in the world!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-how-to-get-from-monteverde-to-manuel-antonio\">How to get from Monteverde to Manuel Antonio<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<h5 id=\"h-by-car-1\"><strong>By car<\/strong>:<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>It is an easy 4-hour drive from Monteverde to Manuel Antonio. However, all the roads are good, and you will not need a 4&#xD7;4 car. About halfway, make a quick stop at the famous<a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/pFnMvmiymcDAsgP5A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"> Crocodile Bridge<\/a>, where you have a good chance of spotting crocodiles. Please do not buy any meat from the sellers because this interferes with the crocodile&#x2019;s natural feeding habits. Plus, according to Costa Rican Law, <em>you are prohibited from feeding wildlife.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Read:<\/strong><em> <\/em>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/wildlife-tourism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Things to know about wildlife tourism<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h5 id=\"h-by-bus-or-shuttle-1\"><strong>By bus or shuttle<\/strong>:<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>Unfortunately, there&#x2019;s no direct bus from Monteverde to Manuel Antonio. Instead, take the Santa Elena (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Manuel Antonio<\/a>) to Puntarenas bus and change bus to Quepos. Once in Quepos, change buses to Manuel Antonio. The total journey will take about 6-8 hours and cost about 10 USD.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, book a direct shuttle between both destinations. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transport-monteverde-manuelantonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See the shuttle options here<\/a>)<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-where-to-stay-in-manuel-antonio\">Where to Stay in Manuel Antonio<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The closer your accommodation is to Manuel Antonio National Park, the more expensive it gets. Therefore, we recommend staying between Quepos and the national park if you have your own transport. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/manuel-antonio-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all your hotel options here<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/the-falls-manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"The Falls Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/15000631\/the-falls-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">The Falls Hotel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/teva-manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Teva Hostel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/15000622\/teva-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Teva Hostel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-10-manuel-antonio\">Day 10: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Manuel Antonio<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Spend your day in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Manuel Antonio National Park<\/a>, one of the most beautiful natural areas in the world! Although it&#x2019;s home to hundreds of different species, it&#x2019;s also one of the smallest national parks, making it easy to explore on a day trip. Buy a ticket to enter the park and hike one of the many trails, looking for exciting animals like macaws, iguanas, sloths, and squirrel monkeys. We recommend taking a guided tour so you can get to learn heaps more about the diversity of the wildlife, flora, and fauna in this area.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week travel guide manuel antonio beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"245\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week travel guide manuel antonio beach\" class=\"wp-image-77618 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1394px) 100vw, 1394px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39.jpg 1394w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-436x600.jpg 436w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-588x810.jpg 588w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-245x338.jpg 245w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-118x163.jpg 118w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-131x180.jpg 131w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-558x768.jpg 558w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-743x1024.jpg 743w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-784x1080.jpg 784w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-1046x1440.jpg 1046w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-300x413.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-600x826.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-150x207.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212636\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-39.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Once you walk through the jungle trails, you&#x2019;ll arrive at the paradise Manuel Antonio Beach (many people buy a ticket to enter the park just to spend the day here). Because these beaches are protected, they&#x2019;re absolutely pristine, with the whitest sand and bluest water. Relax on the beach, listening to the sound of coconuts in the breeze while you spot iguanas roaming freely across the sand.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">More about<\/strong>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/manuel-antonio\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Manuel Antonio National Park in Costa Rica<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-77622 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03212706\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-41-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static