nourhair.com\/costa-rica\/nauyaca-waterfalls\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">about the Nauyaca Waterfalls<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week itinerary nauyaca waterfall\"><\/noscript><img width=\"248\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica 2 week itinerary nauyaca waterfall\" class=\"wp-image-77636 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1409px) 100vw, 1409px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1.jpg 1409w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1-440x600.jpg 440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1-594x810.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1-248x338.jpg 248w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1-120x163.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1-132x180.jpg 132w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1-564x768.jpg 564w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1-751x1024.jpg 751w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03220516\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-38-1-793x1080.jpg 793w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-cont