azypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03210409\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-27.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-14-drive-back-to-san-jose-departure\">Day 14: Drive back to San Jose (Departure)<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After an amazing 2 weeks in Costa Rica, it&#x2019;s time to say goodbye to this beautiful country, taking with you all the fantastic memories of your adventure. On the last day of your Costa Rica itinerary, make your way back to SJO airport (a 3.5-hour drive from Uvita). Alternatively, if you have a flight late in the day, you could visit one more waterfall (like La Paz, which is an hour north of the city).<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>If you need a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/san-jose-airport-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">hotel close to the airport<\/a>, stay at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/san-jose-airport-hotels\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Alajuela<\/a> instead of San Jose.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03202622\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-24.jpg\" alt=\"2 week travel guide costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" 