9;re planning on traveling to more remote areas too.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>If you&#x2019;re planning to rent a car in Costa Rica, we recommend using <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a> because all insurances needed are included in the price <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">displayed on their website<\/a>. No hidden costs.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-by-jeep-with-tent-or-campervan\"><strong>By Jeep with Tent or Campervan<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>For an unforgettable adventure, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/camping-costa-rica\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">rent a 4&#xD7;4 jeep in Costa Rica<\/a>! This is the most incredible experience, as you sleep under the stars, moving from place to place, and finding some gorgeous hidden spots.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Best of all, renting a 4&#xD7;4 jeep gives you the option to drive through national parks and cross rivers in Corcovado and Guanacaste areas. Although the rental price might seem expensive, it&#x2019;s worth remembering that this is your accommodation, transport, and kitchen all in one. Because of this, your trip might actually end up cheaper!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n