ener\">rental car<\/a>. However, if you travel with two or more people, you can split accommodation and transport costs.&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-budget\">\n        <span class=\"block-budget__title\">Budget<\/span><ul class=\"block-budget__list\"><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hotel: 50 &#x2013; 150 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hostel: 10 &#x2013; 180 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--restaurants\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Price per meal: 15 &#x2013; 30 USD\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Entrances: 125 &#x2013; 250 USD \/ week\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Transport: 600 &#x2013; 1000 USD \/ week\n                    <\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Budget tip!<\/strong> The currency in Costa Rica is Colones. Save on exchange fees by converting your own local currency to Colones with a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Wise card<\/a>. You can use this card to withdraw Colonos from the ATM in Costa Rica or pay by card at most shops. Some restaurants charge USD by default, but it will significantly affect the total bill if you ask them to charge Colones. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Get a Wise card here; it&#x2019;s free!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03165444\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-7.jpg\" alt=\"budget tips costa rica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"budget tips costa rica\" class=\"wp-image-77473 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03165444\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-7.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03165444\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03165444\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03165444\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-7-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03165444\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/031