gure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The end of April to the end of November is the rainy season, with the most rain in October. However, don&#x2019;t let this affect your choice as it never rains for long, only a few short rain showers each day. The rain also makes nature incredibly luscious! In addition, this period is much cheaper; you could even save a third of your total budget by traveling during this time.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/costa-rica\/puerto-viejo\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Puerto Viejo<\/a> is on the Caribbean coast and has slightly different seasons. August to October are generally dry, unlike other parts of Costa Rica.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03215444\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-42.jpg\" alt=\"costa rica travel 2 week itinerary nauyaca waterfall \"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"costa rica travel 2 week itinerary nauyaca waterfall \" class=\"wp-image-77630 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03215444\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-