pener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Check here if you need a visa to enter<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-is-costa-rica-safe\">Is Costa Rica Safe?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Costa Rica is very safe for tourists, with some of the friendliest locals globally. It also has the lowest rate of violent crimes in all of Central America. However, like most countries in Latin America, it does have a few problems with drug trafficking, poverty, and pickpockets. Always keep your belongings within eyesight and exercise caution. This way, you&#x2019;re unlikely to experience any issues.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/travel-safety\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tips on how to travel Travel Safe<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03215955\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-36.jpg\" alt=\"is costa rica safe\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"is costa rica safe\" class=\"wp-image-77634 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03215955\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-36.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/03215955\/Costa-Rica-2-week-itinerary-36-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c